This is the README file for Lingua::ZH::Summarize, a simple module
providing summarization of Chinese texts.

* Installation

Lingua::ZH::Summarize uses the standard perl module install process:

cpansign -v		# see SIGNATURE for details
perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

